## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of online resources and the potential bias in historical accounts. Many acts of resistance were not documented, especially those that were covert or unsuccessful. Additionally, the perspectives of enslaved individuals themselves are often underrepresented in historical records, which can skew the understanding of resistance strategies. Further research using primary sources and narratives from former slaves could provide a more comprehensive view.